# [[Myanmar]]; a country in [[Southeast Asia]], on the west coast of the [[w:Indochina Peninsula]].

====Usage====
{{rfc-header|Usage|lang=en}}
''Burma'' is a traditional name of [[Myanmar]], and was the official name until 1989.  It is still used to express disapproval of the current military government which changed the name.

